// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1047 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bb26c446-3a22-54a3-bfd6-bddf2de0fc55

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
